headline: Un-carrier Un-wrapped 2024
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., December 18, 2024--As 2024 winds down, it’s the perfect time to relive the highlights that made this year epic — like binge-watching "The Bear," streaming "Espresso" on repeat and embracing the sweet T-Life. As we get ready for everything that 2025 has in store, let’s take a look back at some of the biggest T-Mobile milestones that made 2024 a year to remember.
